                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/28d1c4b4b05f4ae6341677e5b4fc4ae3_3155326041002840323.png",
                      "menu_id": 18,
                      "name": "Gales of Reverie",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "การต่อสู้อย่างจริงจัง",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "แนะนำด่าน",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"แค่เกมแบบนี้ ก็ทำให้เธอมีความสุขได้มากขนาดนั้นแล้วเหรอ? เด็กน้อยจริง ๆ... ถ้ายากเล่นก็ให้ไวให้ว่องหน่อย\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(236, 229, 216)"
                      ],
                      "text": "[กฎพิเศษ] ในตอนเริ่ม \"ผู้พเนจร\" จะติดตั้งการ์ดพรสวรรค์ \"Gales of Reverie\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "ทีมของคู่ต่อสู้",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4365,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/144837601/ce89cee858b7e18759cc60ce9eb7657b_536631679454833307.png",
